sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant View as MapView (mapa / mapa_dane)
    participant DB as Database
    participant JS as MapRenderer

    %% =========================
    %% INITIAL MAP LOAD
    %% =========================
    User ->> Browser: Open map page
    Browser ->> View: GET /miejsca/mapa/
    View -->> Browser: HTML + JS

    Browser ->> JS: Initialize map

    %% =========================
    %% USER APPLIES FILTERS
    %% =========================
    User ->> JS: Set filters (typ, distance, day)

    JS ->> View: GET /miejsca/mapa/dane/?filters...

    %% =========================
    %% BACKEND PROCESSING
    %% =========================
    alt Filtering places (UC-22)
        View ->> DB: Query Miejsce with filters (typ, distance)
        DB -->> View: Filtered Miejsce records
    end

    alt Filtering discounts (UC-23)
        View ->> DB: Query Znizka + related Miejsce by day
        DB -->> View: Matching discounted places
    end

    %% =========================
    %% RESPONSE
    %% =========================
    View -->> JS: JSON (places with optional discount info)

    %% =========================
    %% RENDERING
    %% =========================
    JS ->> JS: render_markers()
    JS -->> Browser: Display markers on map

    Browser -->> User: Map with filtered places and/or discounts